Bullheaded			CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:Regional.LevelOneFeatOnly	VISIBLE:EXPORT									PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,TYPE=Regional],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Bullheaded]							PREMULT:1,[PREMULT:2,[PRERACE:1,Dwarf],[PREREGION:Underdark (Earthroot)],[PREREGION:Underdark (Northdark)],[PREREGION:Great Rift],[PREREGION:Spine of the World]],[PREMULT:2,[PRERACE:1,Human],[PREREGION:Altumbel],[PREREGION:Damara],[PREREGION:Great Dale],[PREREGION:Rashemen],[PREREGION:Western Heartlands]],[PREMULT:2,[PRERACE:1,Taer],[PREREGION:Icerim Mountains]]																																																						DESC:The stubbornness and determination of your kind are legendary. You are exceptionally headstrong and difficult to sway from your course.																																															ASPECT:Immunity|Shaken Condition																					ASPECT:SaveBonus|Immune to the Shaken condition	BONUS:SAVE|Will|2																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.37		DESC:You receive a +2 bonus on all Will saves. You cannot become shaken, and you ignore the effects of the shaken condition.
