Dreadful Wrath		CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:Regional.LevelOneFeatOnly	VISIBLE:EXPORT									PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,TYPE=Regional],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Dreadful Wrath]							PREMULT:1,[PREMULT:2,[PRERACE:1,Human],[PREREGION:Rashemen]],[PREMULT:2,[PRERACE:1,Kir-lanan],[PREREGION:Far Hills]],[PREMULT:2,[PRERACE:1,Kuo-toa],[PREREGION:Underdark (Sloopdilmonpolop)]],[PREMULT:2,[PRERACE:1,RACESUBTYPE=Planetouched],[PREREGION:Impiltur],[PREREGION:Silver Marches],[PREREGION:Thay],[PREREGION:Western Heartland]]																																																													DESC:You are terrible to behold in battle, and few foes have the heart to face you without quailing.																																																						ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dreadful Wrath ~ Frightful Presence																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.38		DESC:When you charge, make a full attack, or cast a spell that either targets an enemy or includes an enemy in its area, you gain the frightful presence ability for that round. Each enemy within a 20-foot radius of you must succeed on a Will save (DC 10 + 1/2 your character level + your Cha modifier) or be shaken for 1 minute. Regardless of its success or failure on the saving throw, any creature exposed to this effect is immune to your frightful presence for the next 24 hours. This is an extraordinary morale effect. Special: You may select this feat only as a 1st-level character. You may have only one regional feat.
